'''Agezlan awraɣ''' neɣ '''Itran n welkam agejdan anaw-G''' d [[itri]] seg [[Alkam agejdan|welkam agejdan]] yeṭṭafaren [[Asesmel atraw|talmest taylalant]] '''G''' yakk d tseddart n [[asfijjej (tasnallunt)|usfijjej]] '''V'''. Takura tamudemant n yitran am wid-ak-a tga gar n 0,8 alamma d 1,2 n [[takura tanafukt|tkurawin tinafukin]] akken i lan (sɛan) [[taẓɣelt|taẓɣelt tajummant]] yattawaṭen seg 5,300 alamma d 6000 C°.<ref name="hh">[http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1981A&AS...46..193H Empirical bolometric corrections for the main-sequence], G. M. H. J. Habets and J. R. W. Heintze, ''Astronomy and Astrophysics Supplement'' '''46''' (November 1981), pp. 193–237. {{Webarchive|url=http://web.archive.org/web/20171109220215/http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1981A%26AS...46..193H |date=09 wamber 2017}}</ref> dɣa itran n telmest G atnan di tallit n usuɣel n [[Hudṛujin|u hidrujin]] ɣer [[Ahilium]] deg weɣyay-is s temhalt n [[Azday aɣisan|wezday aɣisan]] i d-ittilin deh yitran n [[Alkam agejdan|welkam agejdan]] yakk.<ref name="valpo">[http://physics.valpo.edu/courses/a101/notes/070409_LowMass.pdf Stellar Evolution: Main Sequence to Giant], class notes, Astronomy 101, [[Valparaiso University]], accessed on line June 19, 2007. {{Assaɣ yerrẓen|azemz= mayu 2019 |bot=JarBot}} {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200513165316/http://physics.valpo.edu/courses/a101/notes/070409_LowMass.pdf |date=13 mayu 2020}}</ref>
Tafukt tga d amedya igerrzen yerna d win i d-yufraren yakk deg tegrawt n yitran n G. Yal yiwet n [[tasint|tsint]] yettili-d wezday n wazal n 600 n imelyan n iṭunnen seg [[Hidṛujin|uhidṛuj]] ɣer [[hilium|uhilium]], ayen yettarran azal n 4 n imelyan n iṭunnen seg [[Tanga|tenga]] ɣer [[tafasa|tfasa]].<ref>[http://www.astronomy.ohio-state.edu/~ryden/ast162_1/notes2.html Why Does The Sun Shine?], lecture, Barbara Ryden, Astronomy 162, [[Taseddawit n uwanek n Ohio]], accessed on line June 19, 2007. {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170806223611/http://www.astronomy.ohio-state.edu/~ryden/ast162_1/notes2.html |date=06 ɣuct 2017}}</ref>
